  "body": "\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to buy cryptos using LocalCryptos on the Buy Crypto webview.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: The webview from the Buy Crypto feature doesn't give us web3 access to the wallet, and LocalCryptos need it.\r\nIf we go on LocalCryptos.com using the web3 browser, everything works pretty nice. They even have a good integration with Status, showing our logo.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nIt should allow me to connect with my Status Wallet form the webview.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nIt doesn't allow me to connect with my Status Wallet form the webview.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to the wallet tab\r\n- Click on \" Buy Crypto\"\r\n- Choose LocalCryptos\r\n- Try to connect your wallet\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n*Summary*: Make sure the Buy Crypto webview let me connect to my wallet when I need to.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: v1.12\r\n* Operating System: Android and IOS\r\n\r\n",
